project_descr: This project aims to promote knowledge and awareness in Human Development in oPt.  It is part of a multi-phased programme designed for advocacy in oPt as per UNDP's contribution to setting the development agenda and supporting development debate.

outputs.output_descr: The NHDR project will be implemented in three tracks. It  involves the preparation of the NHDR itself, cover the carrying out of the quarterly surveys on perceptions and the production of Human Development materials and programme development support.
